# Golden Toolbox — Business Checkup environment variables
# Copy this file to `.env` and fill in real values. `.env` is gitignored.
# In production, set these in Vercel → Project → Settings → Environment Variables.

# --- Google PageSpeed Insights (FREE, no billing) — priority #2 ---
PAGESPEED_API_KEY=

# --- Google Places / Maps Platform (billing enabled, lives in free credit) — priority #4 ---
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=
# Daily cap on Places "requests" (1 details + 1 text search = 2 per live report) as a cost safety net.
# PLACES_DAILY_CAP=300

# --- Content Quality: Gemini (Google AI Studio FREE tier) — optional ---
# Reads the business's homepage and judges clarity / call-to-action / trust /
# "would a customer hire you". Free within rate limits; get a key at
# https://aistudio.google.com/apikey. If unset (or if the call fails or the
# rate limit is hit), Content Quality falls back to a free pattern-based
# heuristic — the report still renders, just without the LLM narrative.
# Note: on the free tier Google may use inputs to improve models; the only
# input sent is the business's own PUBLIC homepage text.
# GEMINI_API_KEY=
# GEMINI_MODEL=gemini-1.5-flash
#
# The old Directory Presence category (Facebook/Nextdoor/X self-link checks)
# and standalone Tech Stack category were removed: they penalized normal
# trades businesses for not running paid ads or third-party profiles. Yelp
# stays out too — its free Fusion tier was discontinued ($229+/mo).

# --- Upstash Redis (free tier) — cache + rate limits + spend log — priority #7 ---
# When BOTH are set, the store switches from deterministic mock mode to Upstash.
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_URL=
# UPSTASH_REDIS_REST_TOKEN=

# --- Admin manual-trigger secret — priority #8 ---
# Any long random string; used as the x-admin-secret header.
# ADMIN_SECRET=

# --- Lead notification to you (already live) ---
# Defaults to the existing Formspree endpoint if unset. Formspree only
# supports a single fixed recipient on the free plan — its _cc and
# _autoresponse fields were tested and both reject the whole submission on
# this plan, so they're not used. To change who Formspree notifies, add/edit
# the recipient in the Formspree dashboard itself, not here.
# FORMSPREE_ENDPOINT=https://formspree.io/f/mgojwopl

# --- Direct owner notification email (free, 3,000/mo, no billing) — a
# second, independent channel alongside Formspree above, sent to you the
# moment any report finishes. Uses Resend's sandbox sender
# (onboarding@resend.dev), which needs NO domain verification as long as
# OWNER_EMAIL is the same address as your Resend account login.
RESEND_API_KEY=
# OWNER_EMAIL=hello@sarza.ai
# RESEND_FROM=Golden Toolbox <onboarding@resend.dev>
